                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ظِلٍّ﴾ هُوَ دُخَانُ جَهَنَّمَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿ذِي ثَلاَثِ شُعَبٍ﴾ يَتَفَرَّعُ مِنْهُ ثَلاَثُ قِطَعٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "77:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لاَ ظَلِيلٍ﴾ لاَ يُظِلُّ مِنْ حَرِّ ذَلِكَ اليَوْمِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَلاَ يُغْنِي﴾ لاَ يَدْفَعُ، وَلاَ يَقِي.</h2>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "77:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿بِشَرَرٍ﴾ الشَّرَارَةُ: مَا يَتَطَايَرُ مِنَ النَّارِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿كَالْقَصْرِ﴾ كَالبِنَاءِ المُشَيَّدِ فِي العِظَمِ وَالاِرْتِفَاعِ.</p>"
        },
        "33": {
